<dt>
<b><u><font color="#000000">May/June 2002</font></u></b></dt>

<dt>
<font color="#000000"></font></dt>

<dt>
<font color="#000000">At the end of this month I am going to Greece, Spain
and Italy. In Greece I plan to visit Mihalis Kolountzakis, who lives in
Iraklion, Crete. In Spain, I plan to visit Fernando Soria and other harmonic
analysts at the Universidad Autonoma. In Italy, I plan to give a talk at
the special session in harmonic analysis organized by Fulvio Ricci and
Elias Stein. I will then travel to Padova to give a series of lectures
to graduate students. I will return from this trip at the end of June.
Zara will join me in Italy and Spain. My flight information is the following:</font></dt>

